<h4><font color="#408080"><a name="instructions">General Instructions</a></font></h4>

<p>Enter your name, address and social security number (and your spouse's if you file a
joint return), and your employment and financial information.</p>

<p>Also answer the questions and enter your monthly expenses.&nbsp; Be sure to indicate
the amount you can pay each month and select the number of months you will need to
complete your payment agreement.</p>

<hr>

<h4><font color="#408080"><a name="paper">Requesting an Income Tax Installment Payment
Agreement on Paper</a></font></h4>

<p>If you do not wish to request an installment payment agreement using the Internet, you
may download and print <a href="/pdf/1998/inc/dtf383_1998.pdf">Form DTF-383</a> using
Adobe Acrobat. &nbsp;If you do not have Adobe Acrobat, you may <a href="/forms/adobe.htm">download
it free</a> from this website. </p>

<p>You may also obtain this form using the Tax Department's Fax on Demand system.&nbsp;
You can access this system by dialing <nobr>(800) 748-3676</nobr>, 24 hours a day.&nbsp; An index of
Fax forms and their codes is available on the Department's website. </p>

<p>You can also request this form from our Forms Request System.&nbsp; You can reach this
system by calling <nobr>(800) 462-8100</nobr>.</p>

